1 indi gents, whose telephone number shall be posted within the city or
2 county jail facility;
3 2. A bail bondsman; and
4 3. A relative or other person chosen by the arrested person.
5 The telephone calls shall be provided immediately upon request, or
6 as soon thereafter as practicable.
7 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
